verbose_text: A Placebo Controlled, Double-Blind, Parallel Arm Trial to Assess the Efficacy of Dronedarone 400 mg bid for the Prevention of Cardiovascular Hospitalization or Death from Any Cause in Patients with Atrial Fibrillation / Atrial Flutter (ATHENA) was conducted to determine if dronedarone could decrease the composite end point of cardiovascular hospitalizations or death in patients with atrial fibrillation.
evidence: dronedarone could decrease the composite end
